title: Chickpea salad with sun-dried tomatoes and feta
ingredients: ['1 (400g) tin chickpeas, drained', '55g oil-packed sun-dried tomatoes, drained and sliced into strips', '250g feta cheese, crumbled', '1 red onion, finely chopped', '2 cloves garlic, minced', '1 tablespoon freshly chopped coriander', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '2 tablespoons lemon juice', 'salt to taste']
